profile:
With 15+ years of experience in water damage restoration, we understand that your family and home are the two most important investments in your life, which is why at Fresh Start Restoration we are committed to providing our customers with the fastest and most professional disaster restoration services in the industry. 

Let us give you the Fresh Start you deserve!

* Following all Covid-19 safety protocols

Call us now: (778) 552-9114

-Indoor & Outdoor Remodeling
-Kitchen Renovation
-Bathroom Renovation
-Basement Finishing & Renovation
-Laneway Houses
-Secondary Suites
